bilingual.source: After he graduated from medical college in 1916, Bethune worked as a doctor in England, the US, and Canada.
bilingual.target: 1916年从医学院毕业后，白求恩在英国、美国和加拿大当医生。

bilingual.source: Eight years later, Lin graduated from Peking Union Medical College (PUMC) with the Wenhai Scholarship, the highest prize given to graduates.
bilingual.target: 八年后，林巧稚以毕业生最高奖——文海奖学金从北京协和医学院毕业。
他在学院里结识了很多朋友。

bilingual.source: He decided to apply to a normal college.
He studies cooking at a training college.
bilingual.target: 他在职业学院学习烹饪。
我们的学院有一个很大的图书馆。

bilingual.source: She dreams of getting into a top college.
bilingual.target: 她梦想进入一所顶尖的学院。

bilingual.source: This college offers a variety of courses.
bilingual.target: 这个学院提供多种专业课程。

bilingual.source: My brother studies at a famous college.
bilingual.target: 我哥哥在一所著名的学院学习。

bilingual.source: She is a sessional lecturer at the college.
bilingual.target: 她是这所学院的学期的讲师。

list.abstract: college（英[ˈkɒlɪdʒ]，美[ˈkɑːlɪdʒ]），英语单词。词性是名词，释义为大学；专科学校；职业学校。例句：Below are several tips to ease (使熟悉) yourself into college life.（下面是让你熟悉大学生活的几个建议）。 近义词为university、academy、campus。
中文名《大学预备生》，是一部出自美国的喜剧片。

yingyinNormal.en: At Harvard's commencement tomorrow as your dean described, each school is gonna stand up and graduate together, the college, the law school, the med school and so on.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们院长也讲了，在明天的哈佛毕业典礼上，每个学院都要起立并一同毕业。本科部、法学院、医学院等等。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《Facebook COO谢丽尔·桑德伯格哈佛演讲》

yingyinNormal.en: King's College, Cambridge. Now, it says here you were a bit of a prodigy in the maths department.
yingyinNormal.zh: 剑桥大学，国王学院。这上面写着你在数学系算是个天才。

yingyinNormal.en: But what's curious, is he's not actually missing. This is Professor Arnold. At Imperial College, this morning.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但让人好奇的是，他并未真正失踪。这就是阿尔诺德教授。今天早上出现在帝国理工学院。

yingyinNormal.en: We know that in today's economy whether you go to a four-year college, a community college or a professional training program, some higher education is the surest ticket to the middle class.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们都知道，在当今的经济环境中，你是否上过完整的大学、社区学院或参加过职业培训直接关系到你能否跻身中产阶级。

yingyinNormal.en: My first boss out of college was Lant Pritchett, an economist who teaches at the Kennedy School who is here with us today.
yingyinNormal.zh: 本科后我的第一任老板是兰特·普里切特。肯尼迪学院授课的一位经济学家。他今天也在现场。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《Facebook COO谢丽尔·桑德伯格哈佛演讲》

yingyinNormal.en: I know a lot of students here at Oxford have your own separate bedrooms, but when I was a freshman at Williams College, I was not so fortunate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道这里，牛津的许多学生有自己单独的卧室，但我进入威廉姆斯学院的时候，我没有那么幸运。

yingyinNormal.en: No way. That's a great idea. Which school, Ridgemont or Faber? Fast Times at Ridgemont High, not John Hughes. It's a trap. Faber College from Animal House.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不会吧。这主意太棒了。哪所学校，雷奇蒙德还是费伯？《雷奇蒙德中学时光》不是约翰·休斯导的。这是个陷阱。费伯学院则在《动物屋》。

yingyinNormal.en: Excuse me? I'm just wondering if you really gave it the old college try. Or in your case, the old community college try.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说什么？我只是在想，如果你能试试旧学院派的做法，或者就你而言，旧社区大学的做法。

yingyinNormal.en: First job out of college is critical, kid.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小子，大学毕业后的第一份工作至关重要。

yingyinNormal.en: I made out with two chicks once in college.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我大学期间和两个女生乱搞过。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, fucking some college guy. Oh, fuck you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是，所以你和那个大学狗搞上了。搞你妹的。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm in college, and I'm in a band. Yeah, okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是大学生，还是乐队成员。那好吧。

yingyinNormal.en: What if I got married instead of going to college?
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我不去上大学而是结婚 那会怎么样?

yingyinNormal.en: Come on, was it somebody maybe you dated in college?
yingyinNormal.zh: 她会是你大学时的女朋友吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I can't believe it. I'm officially a college student!
yingyinNormal.zh: 不可思议，我正式成为大学生了！

yingyinNormal.en: Got myself a Mr. Sam Witwicky, recent college graduate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 来了一个山姆威特维奇先生，刚毕业。

yingyinNormal.en: Which college? Ed's Learning Hole. Really? No! I am donezo.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哪所大学？艾德的学习之洞。真的吗？不是！我完了。

yingyinNormal.en: College? Pennington High School.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大学？彭宁顿中学。

yingyinNormal.en: The whole thing started in a college dorm room. And if you look around, you might think you're still in college.
yingyinNormal.zh: 整个灵感起源于一间大学宿舍，而如果你四处看看的话，你可能会觉得你仿佛还在大学里。

yingyinNormal.en: Sending Samantha off to college. Sending you off to college. You know what's next? Huh? It's my fucking funeral.
yingyinNormal.zh: 送萨曼塔上大学，送你上大学。你知道下一个里程碑是什么吗？嗯？是我他妈的葬礼。

examination_example.sentence: While high school does not generally encourage students to explore new aspects of life, <highlight>college</highlight> sets the stage for that exploration.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虽然高中一般不鼓励学生探索生活的新方面，但大学为这种探索奠定了基础。

examination_example.sentence: A latest study on the <highlight>college</highlight> job market showed that employers wanted to hire 22% fewer graduates this year than last.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一项关于大学就业市场的最新研究显示，雇主今年希望招聘的毕业生比去年减少了22%。

examination_example.sentence: Beaver Stadium, State <highlight>College</highlight>, Pennsylvania, U.S. Capacity: 106,572.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国宾夕法尼亚州州立学院比弗体育场。可容纳人数：106572人。

examination_example.sentence: Kyle Field, <highlight>College</highlight> Station, Texas, U.S. Capacity: 102,512.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国德克萨斯州大学城，凯尔体育场。可容纳人数：102512人。

examination_example.sentence: During my second year at the city <highlight>college</highlight>, I was told that the education department was offering a "free" course.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我在市立大学读二年级时，有人告诉我，教育系提供一门“免费”课程。

数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
